import React from 'react'
import CarouselHome from './Components/CarouselHome'
import Banner from './Components/Banner'
import Banner2 from './Components/Banner2'

const HomePage = () => {
  return (
    <>
      <CarouselHome/>
      <Banner/>
      <Banner2/>
   
    </>
  )
}

export default HomePage
